<li><a href="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-5353866757306368589" class="external text" title="http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-5353866757306368589" rel="nofollow">"Epicurus on Happiness"</a> - A documentary on the philosophy of Epicurus, first 11:25 of below, Greek subtitles.</li>
